import React from 'react'
import { LoginSignUpWrapper, WrapperTitleText,WrapperTitle, FormContainer, SlideControlsLoginLabel, SlideControlsSignupLabel,
    SlideControlsSliderTab, WrapperSlideControls, FormInnerFormField, FormInnerFormPassLink, FormInnerFormSignUpLink, ButtonLayer,
    FormInnerFormFieldInput, Button, FormContainerFormInner, FormContainerFormInnerForm, FormInnerFormPassLinkA, FormInnerFormSignUpLinkA,
    FullContainer,} from './LoginSignUpElements'

const LoginSignUp = () => {
  return (
    <FullContainer>
        <LoginSignUpWrapper>
            <WrapperTitleText>
                <WrapperTitle>
                    <SlideControlsLoginLabel>Login Form</SlideControlsLoginLabel>
                </WrapperTitle>
                <WrapperTitle>
                    <SlideControlsSignupLabel>Signup Form</SlideControlsSignupLabel>
                </WrapperTitle>
            </WrapperTitleText>
            <FormContainer>
                <WrapperSlideControls>
                    <input type="radio" style={{display:'none'}} name="slide" id="login" checked></input>
                    <input type="radio" style={{display:'none'}} name="slide" id="signup"></input>
                    <SlideControlsLoginLabel for="login">Login</SlideControlsLoginLabel>
                    <SlideControlsSignupLabel for="signup">Signup</SlideControlsSignupLabel>
                    <SlideControlsSliderTab></SlideControlsSliderTab>
                </WrapperSlideControls>
                <FormContainerFormInner>
                    <FormContainerFormInnerForm action="#" class="login">
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="text" placeholder="Email Address" required></FormInnerFormFieldInput>
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="password" placeholder="Password" required></FormInnerFormFieldInput>
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormPassLink>
                           <FormInnerFormPassLinkA href="google.com">Forgot password?</FormInnerFormPassLinkA>
                        </FormInnerFormPassLink>
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <Button>
                                <ButtonLayer></ButtonLayer>
                                <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="submit" value="Login"></FormInnerFormFieldInput>
                            </Button>
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormSignUpLink>
                            Not a member? <FormInnerFormSignUpLinkA href="google.com">Signup now</FormInnerFormSignUpLinkA>
                        </FormInnerFormSignUpLink>
                    </FormContainerFormInnerForm>
                    <FormContainerFormInnerForm action="#" class="signup">
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="text" placeholder="Email Address" required />
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="password" placeholder="Password" required />
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="password" placeholder="Confirm password" required />
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                        <FormInnerFormField>
                            <Button>
                                <ButtonLayer></ButtonLayer>
                                <FormInnerFormFieldInput type="submit" value="Signup"></FormInnerFormFieldInput>
                            </Button>
                        </FormInnerFormField>
                    </FormContainerFormInnerForm>
                </FormContainerFormInner>
            </FormContainer>
        </LoginSignUpWrapper>
    </FullContainer>
  );
};

export default LoginSignUp;
